}},{"id":"773fa5a54f","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来 陈伯达 康生","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"97d543fa2c","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.04.12","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bf881b40b0","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：一九六七年四月十二日二十三时五分至十二日一时四十五分。地点：人大会堂安徽厅。接见人：总理、伯达、康生、肖华、张春桥、王力、关锋、姚文元及总政，总参和各大军区负责人徐立清、李天佑、韩先楚、宋任穷、张国华、陈先瑞等。被接见人：区党委代表：高锦明、权星桓、康修民、李树德、李质、郭以清、张鲁。军区代表：吴涛、刘华香、肖应棠、黄厚、刘昌、王良太、姜文启、诸方玉、敖长锁和独立二师杨饱松、尤亚民、华民等。军区造反派代表：邵仲康等24人。呼三司等革命造反派代表：高树华、郝广德等57人。红卫军等保守组织代表：张三林等9人。王铎、王逸伦没让参加。〗","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3b111e1d0c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在开会，内蒙古情况大致清楚了，已经两个多月了嘛！今天请后来的同志再谈谈。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"147a0d5cc9","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：（给总理介绍）这是张孝同志。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78e8930954","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那个学校的（翻材料）？","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2dbeacbb19","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：“火车头”的。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af699df004","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有名字没有（指是否登记过）？","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3185654a74","type":"paragraph","text":"赵刚，宋学孔：没有，今天才来的。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90a5110f2e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那一部分的？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5da66c99d8","type":"paragraph","text":"郝广德：“火车头”的。（张孝说了一句，声音很低）","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0166b21c6b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你能说话吗？火车头代表替他说说。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"472d479c83","type":"paragraph","text":"张孝：能！（旁边两人扶起）","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7ec2e5246","type":"paragraph","text":"总理，康生：坐下吧！坐下吧！","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7f469a5af","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不是还有一位火车头的同志嘛？","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"377c09b3d1","type":"paragraph","text":"包长胜：有，我叫包长胜。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"51180759f1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你替他谈一谈吧。（包讲张孝受迫害经过，谈到残废时）","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"97f6ab336f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：治不好了吗？快送到北京医院！","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7cbf367f76","type":"paragraph","text":"张孝：我说两句。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8f44114fd","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：坐着说吧！（总理抬起头）你谈吧！（对赵刚）快点送医院去看看。（张孝：控诉被迫害经过）","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b6c1a3633","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：他讲的与事实不符，他们写过反动标语。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9bb95ce8af","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么标语？","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4c7d84014","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：“青松不怕火烧，‘火纵’不怕狗咬”，攻击解放军。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b289c6e152","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：就为这件事，应该不应该把人打成这个样子？","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b124bf37c1","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：谁打的，我不清楚。要严惩凶手，我们要为受害者申诉。（大家冷笑）","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed0e36a961","type":"paragraph","text":"（包长胜：严厉驳斥曹文生等人在资本主义反革命复辟逆流中破坏“抓革命，促生产”等罪恶活动。）","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"43f35daece","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对曹文生）我问你，现在为什么不放人？这是不是事实？！","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34dd6c2473","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：据说是放了。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a3205ae31","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：就因为这条标语就抓人？","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"059f3c23e0","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：写的是反动标语。","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"98e9466be1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这样的标语，在北京都有，怎么能是反动标语呢？怎么能是攻击解放军呢？","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e455c23448","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：没有说解放军嘛！解放军你们说拥护，中央指示你们拥护不拥护？","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1420373604","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：拥护！","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"21739c8c9f","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：拥护为什么到现在还不放人？","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1461671e00","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：拥护？！早就说了，你们到现在还不放人。","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dba173c6ed","type":"paragraph","text":"高利陶（军区宣传部干事）：揭发张三林造谣惑众的事实。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"68bb5c06d7","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：我不愿解释个人问题。（众笑）","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab6d07dc3e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是不是三司的？","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7dd0bc0264","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：不是，我是红卫军的，橡胶厂的。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a4cf641150","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：先说这件事，你回答这个问题：为什么还不放人？","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8b7ce09980","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：下午曾打过加急长途电话。他们制造停车事件，他们是不符合公安六条的。","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76886e963c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那一条？你们扣了几个人？","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9f070fbd6","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：八、九个人。","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6feb7e7617","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么时候扣的？","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c76ab1fe6f","type":"paragraph","text":"曹文生：二月五日扣了两个，五个是二月八日扣的。","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1809deea7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：二月八日到现在已有两个多月了，为什么到现在不放？","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e3e6555eb","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：中央命令在你们那里算数不算数？","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f6a38dfc2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：四点指示有效没效？","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6454bbefce","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：有效，今天又打电话回去了。","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6563eaba52","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有郊为什么还不放人？北京的同志来了没有？","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f210fe9d5","type":"paragraph","text":"李天佑：来了。（陈先瑞走到前面去）","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffe8ba9113","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：北京军区是一个小部队，军事接管呼和铁路局。（众：起立高呼：毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！）","index":53,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7b20c6efc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们为什么不放？就算有点嫌疑，已经扣了两个多月了嘛！","index":54,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c39329d6f0","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：抗拒两个多月了嘛！","index":55,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2a4c247ebc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对曹）你还有什么辩护的？（曹文生没吭声的坐下了。）（包长胜继续揭发铁路局两条路线的斗争及曹破坏生产的罪行。）","index":56,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3cd13df032","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：铁路局问题知道了，现在由邮电局王连奎谈谈。王连奎揭×区控制邮电、非法偷听电话等罪行，谈了邮电局二月九日成立保守组织，十号就反夺权。这时总理、康生等首长都笑了）","index":57,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"99096a1d50","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们有几派？","index":58,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"677e52c707","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：两派。","index":59,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"745bbe4739","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们三司观点的有多少人？","index":60,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"818680fd0b","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：我们三司观点的三百人，无产者一百多人。并说二月十号反夺权，他们叫“三结合”。","index":61,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3215ff6607","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他们叫“三结合”？","index":62,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c0dfcae50","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：邮电局还调动农民保权！","index":63,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"373f2f90ed","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：保什么权？多少天？","index":64,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aba588a957","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：三天。","index":65,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e1c8049f2","type":"paragraph","text":"侯凤英：还搞录音。","index":66,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"26dc1073f3","type":"paragraph","text":"众：（他们对打电话都偷听，还延续时间。）（王连奎继续揭发盗用中央名义打电话等）","index":67,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd17becefb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：邮电局驻有多少军队？","index":68,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa93976785","type":"paragraph","text":"王连奎：一个加强连。","index":69,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63bb93847b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在听听地方的。锡盟许名扬同志讲讲。","index":70,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"418ee3e700","type":"paragraph","text":"许名扬：现在还有十三人没放出来。","index":71,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"84c4d644c8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们那里还不放人？","index":72,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f10c703a58","type":"paragraph","text":"许名扬：不放。","index":73,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"15170284a8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么时候问的？","index":74,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f12c44f9cb","type":"paragraph","text":"许名扬：中午问的。","index":75,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f208704e7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：吴涛同志，这个事情交给你解决。","index":76,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"83e6654108","type":"paragraph","text":"（吴涛：马上打电话）","index":77,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aebdcba784","type":"paragraph","text":"（乌盟玉宝讲扣押人的情况，哲盟郭玉讲一人“畏罪自杀”问题。黄宝玉补充哲盟农村资本主义复辟情况。）","index":78,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc535405d5","type":"paragraph","text":"陈振中（巴盟代表）：听说部队支持煤矿夺权后，现在停掌子面。现在三十多人未放，他们说是中央军委指示的。","index":79,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"131a83b79f","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华、王力：这是造谣！","index":80,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"88e7ddfcc2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（叫起兰州司令员说）你们处理。（又对吴涛同志）注意，我们还要和你们单独谈谈。（又问了内蒙日报社情况。）","index":81,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8502f70040","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：报社压制得很厉害，现在军队和红卫军非法占据报社。","index":82,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dfc4ffcdb4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：报社几派？","index":83,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d67b9a2da9","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：报社有保守派吗？","index":84,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7117cda8f0","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：两派。他们还有一百多人。","index":85,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7399b6765","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：报社谁管？","index":86,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05e7fab900","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：他们掌权着呢！","index":87,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33e1bfed4d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：登什么内容？","index":88,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8cd4bc1358","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：没听总理指示，登了地方问题。","index":89,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ff8f244d8","type":"paragraph","text":"众：登“抗大”，登军区。","index":90,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bdae774baf","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有报纸吗？","index":91,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7bc32dd6d","type":"paragraph","text":"李雨楼：没有带，我是从监狱出来直接上火车的。（黄宝玉、高树华等送上两份报纸。）","index":92,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5004443917","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：高树华同志谈谈“联动”情况。","index":93,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f416a51923","type":"paragraph","text":"（高树华谈了中学生中“联动”分子问题。）","index":94,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc5e2e5514","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：让二中讲讲。（二中代表任卫东讲了“联动”罪恶的枪的问题。）","index":95,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6016fda2e2","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：他们还有电台。","index":96,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"779417d67c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：还有电台？有名单吗？给我，有多少人？","index":97,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4bca621b79","type":"paragraph","text":"任卫东：十几个。","index":98,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a0e9589d8","type":"paragraph","text":"高树华：还有反动标语：“打倒康生”等。","index":99,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e314119ad8","type":"paragraph","text":"梁音亭（军区后勤部）：他们游行时打着刘少奇的象。","index":100,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1fbf470782","type":"paragraph","text":"黄宝玉：新华书店一千多张刘少奇的象都被他们拿出来了。","index":101,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a62ebbcb6c","type":"paragraph","text":"众：还举起象高呼口号。","index":102,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3fb7f63eeb","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：我们从新华书店拿出来烧的。","index":103,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f633c68fb","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你们拿着刘少奇的象游行没有？有没有四个象？","index":104,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee2193fadb","type":"paragraph","text":"张三林：不知道。（霍道余揭露他们批判刘少奇是假的）","index":105,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d9b967f22","type":"paragraph","text":"高惠娟：二中赵玉花说，苏修、蒙修支持三司，周总理也支持三司。","index":106,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"19d4e649d6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：捏造！","index":107,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92c35a3002","type":"paragraph","text":"韩文达：他们在火车上审问时说：王力是个大混蛋，是三司的后台，要挖王力的根子。（总理、王力等大笑）","index":108,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4281a138f0","type":"paragraph","text":"曹燕玲（军区红色造反团）：军区文办正在整理王力同志的材料。","index":109,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be3630436d","type":"paragraph","text":"包力陶：怀疑中央的根子，这是军区某些人，他们要挖王力同志的根子。","index":110,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67ec479e91","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：王逸伦的报告是不是都听了？","index":111,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fe4fc8030","type":"paragraph","text":"众：听了。有的是三月三十一日，有的在四月七日。","index":112,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee2f0a6c74","type":"paragraph","text":"包力陶：（详细揭露×区问题）他们说造反派在“一·二二”、“一·二五”事件上是 吃里爬 外。（众站起来指王良太：说过没有？）","index":113,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0bfa1d08fd","type":"paragraph","text":"王良太：说过。","index":114,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74e949bb61","type":"paragraph","text":"（包力陶揭露军区某些领导人造谣蒙蔽群众，刘昌传达反革命策略问题。）","index":115,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"295956bd29","type":"paragraph","text":"康小春：德山（呼市军分区付参谋长）曾念过一个特好消息说：“中央叫各大军区学内蒙。”","index":116,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bfb343b3cc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（手挥一份传单）我这里也有一份，纯属造谣。","index":117,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"238783e279","type":"paragraph","text":"陈永华：今天六点半来电话说：××二师协助保守派对工学院等革命造反派实行武斗。","index":118,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"02b8be903c","type":"paragraph","text":"张鸿喜：我也揭×师情况。……","index":119,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc9b16b8a2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：王志有谈谈。","index":120,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c40032c3f0","type":"paragraph","text":"王志有（八一八）：他们说有两条黑线，一个黑根，要揪李富春、李雪峰、要揪黑根！（回头质问王良太）你说黑根是谁？","index":121,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2bf42379db","type":"paragraph","text":"众：（质问）王良太站起来！（总理没让王讲。）","index":122,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"861cfb0ddc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不要问了，很显然黑根就是中央嘛！","index":123,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"89057d7c60","type":"paragraph","text":"王志有：河西公司反夺权后，报喜时，我们提出意见，说不要让外边的人到厂子里来。他们说是总理点头，林彪同志也在场。","index":124,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c2bd57345b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：真是！造这种谣言。（蔚洋：揭露电台军代表造谣和反夺权问题。）","index":125,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0cf2b67a7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：全部是造谣。","index":126,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6fa1b4af4a","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：造谣。","index":127,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0f9b1a8133","type":"paragraph","text":"蔚洋：他们说，林副主席说：“你们打的不狠，手太软！不如青海，进度不快。”","index":128,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8444d1a16a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：青海文件你们看到没有？","index":129,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"157248466c","type":"paragraph","text":"众：没有。","index":130,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aeca982ffa","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对于顺昌）你们记者有文件，明天给读一读。","index":131,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30321a6281","type":"paragraph","text":"蔚洋：他们造谣说：李天佑根本不支持三司。","index":132,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8179df1937","type":"paragraph","text":"李天佑：我白天去东纵，晚上又从东纵东门到楼上，他们纯属是造谣。","index":133,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c834702a07","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：电台有多少军队？","index":134,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e3332db12e","type":"paragraph","text":"蔚洋：由一个班增至一个排。","index":135,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11d8fcb2af","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：周文孝把农村发枪情况谈谈。","index":136,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"321c2382e4","type":"paragraph","text":"周文孝：给桃花公社发17枝枪，30发子弹。","index":137,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a1d96dbfc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：今天会到此结束了。明天九点钟再开一次，内蒙问题就结束了。让肖华同志与军区同志谈一谈，还有记者和联络员同志同大家谈一谈，还有什么材料送上来，明天开会时间九点。不要再增加了，观点不要说了，已经很清楚了，已经两个多月了嘛！不然人越来越多。群众不要互相对立，不要着急。你们是按毛泽东思想办事的，要等待一下。内蒙古自治区地区大，分区多，还有各旗县，还有牧区，电话传达不到的可以派人嘛！","index":138,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"79b0e7b6c7","type":"paragraph","text":"铁路局去的部队明天天亮就到了。铁路那位同志，明天送到医院，总是可以治好的。","index":139,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba7e26d5e5","type":"paragraph","text":"明天晚上九点开会，有材料还可以送上来。要等待中央的布置。同志们受苦了，这是为革命嘛！我们一定要把边疆的问题解决好。明天结束这个会，要靠革命造反派团结起来。散会。","index":140,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2897f32cb4","type":"paragraph","text":"（全体起立，鼓掌欢送总理及各位首长，总理等招手致意，大家呼口号：毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！）","index":141,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a47b9e391b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}